<P>
<center>
<h2>
 Additional Information<BR>
</h2>
</center>
<P>
<blockquote>
 If hundreds of business organizations nationwide spoke with one
voice, the status quo of big government will be overcome. <BR>

<P>
While the 104th Congress has given small businesses and entrepreneurs
a political climate favorable to change, much work remains in
turning the tide of burdensome taxes and regulations that impede
risk-taking and job creation.<BR>

<P>
Not only do elected officials need to hear regularly from the
business lobby in Washington, but also from business organizations
back home.  <BR>

<P>
If the status quo is left unchallenged, common sense advocates
will be drowned out.<BR>

<P>
<a href="/sbsc/coalition/sbscapp.html">SBS Coalition membership application</a>
<P>
Questions? - <a href="mailto:rstikes@sbsc.org">rstikes@sbsc.org</a><BR>
