<title>Bob Dole</title>
</head>
<body background="/yaf/ground2.gif">
<h1>Bob Dole</h1>
<p>Whether it is in defense of our freedom, our traditional moral values or the free enterprise system, the foundation teaches these beliefs to future generations.  I have worked closely with young men and women trained by your programs, and these fine young people are examples to their peers and society as a whole.</p>
</body>
