<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Many of these upper&#173;income taxpayers
are small businesses &#173;&#173; for example, sole proprietorships,
partnerships, and some subchapter S corporations &#173;&#173;
which file using the personal income tax. Others are entrepreneurs
and wealthy individuals who manage large portfolios of investments.
<P>
