http://www.empower.org:80/heritage/p_review/jan97/homef.html 204.71.237.79 19970210003812 text/html 16653
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:38:50 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 03-Feb-97 21:12:57 GMT
